Culture and Careers at Watts Water

      At Watts Water our culture is reflective of our mission, vision, and values.  Our career opportunities are 
      ideally suited for candidates who can identify with our goals & objectives and demonstrate the skills & abilities reflected in our core competencies. To attract 
      those high-quality individuals we offer a competitive benefits package and opportunities for growth.      
    
Core Competencies
At Watts Water we are committed to attracting, developing, and promoting talented people who help create value for our customers and shareholders.  We use 6 core 
    competencies to evaluate potential associates and assess the performance of our current staff. These core competencies are a direct reflection of our belief that 
    a solid understanding of what’s expected will lead to stronger job performance and satisfaction.   We expect all of our associates to demonstrate their ability and willingness to:

 Collaborate Across Workgroups
 Communicate Effectively
 Deliver High-Quality Work
 Drive for Results
 Focus on the Customer
 Initiate Positive Change



















