Watts Water In Action



Watts Brings Clean Water to Kids in the Philippines
Read More






We group the solutions from our family of companies into five main categories:


Plumbing & Flow Control Solutions





                    The plumbing & flow control solutions from our companies are designed to facilitate efficient water conveyance and control for commercial, residential, and waterworks applications. 
                    




Solutions Include: 





 Backflow prevention devices
 Water regulating devices
 Steam pressure-reducing valves
 Water mixing devices
 PEX plumbing systems
 Gas connectors
 Quick-Connect fittings & manifolds
 Pipeline strainers
 Water shutoff devices
 Water heater installation products

See our Brands & Companies 







Water Quality and Conditioning





                        The water quality & conditioning solutions from our companies are designed to facilitate the testing, treatment, and filtration of water.
                    




Solutions Include: 





 Reverse osmosis systems
 Drinking water filtration
 Water softeners
 Anti-scale solutions
 UV disinfection systems
 Ballast water monitoring systems
 Commercial water filtration
 Water quality monitoring instrumentation
 Foodservice & beverage water filtration

See our Brands & Companies 







Water Reuse & Drainage





                        The water reuse & drainage solutions from our companies are designed to facilitate the management & reuse of storm water and wastewater.
                    




Solutions Include: 





 Cast iron drainage products
 Fixture carrier solutions
 Rainwater harvesting systems
 Stainless steel piping systems
 Interceptor systems
 Acid waste piping systems
 High purity piping 
 Neutralization tanks 
 Stainless steel drainage products

See our Brands & Companies 







HVAC





                    The HVAC solutions from our companies are designed to facilitate occupant comfort and energy efficiency.
                    




Solutions Include: 





 Hydronic heating systems
 Heating & cooling controls
 Electric floor warming systems
 Boiler installation products
 Boilers & water heaters
 Snow & ice melting systems

See our Brands & Companies 







Municipal Waterworks





                    The municipal waterworks solutions from our companies are designed to assist with treating, storing, supplying, and managing the distribution of safe water to a community or region. 
                    




Solutions Include: 





 Backflow prevention devices
 Water regulating devices
 Control valves
 Water quality monitoring instrumentation
 Drinking water filtration
 Water shutoff devices

See our Brands & Companies 








 






 
 





















