Watts Waters’ Americas operation, through its family of companies and brands, provides a wide variety of products and solutions for safely conveying, conserving, and managing water and gas.
Our family of companies offers the following capabilities:

 Comprehensive R&D, from innovative design  to refinement & delivery
 World-class manufacturing operations and state-of-the-art foundry operations
 Deep industry expertise in wide range of product categories & technologies
 Extensive & established distribution network
 Engineering excellence, advanced testing, and manufacturing to support OEM customers
 Retail & wholesaler merchandising support

